
function atan2_top_config(this_block)

  % Revision History:
  %
  %   13-May-2021  (19:21 hours):
  %     Original code was machine generated by Xilinx's System Generator after parsing
  %     /home/franco/seba/doa_test/vec_linalg2/atan_top.v
